{"tid":1929122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三：期待東京奧運按計劃今年7月舉辦　展示全球戰勝疫情","createTime":"2020-03-16T18:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T19:00:08.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"38f4af67871274f490f9d96991b07cb0f4d7210d","tid":1929122,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:42:16.000Z","msg":"日本新增17人感染新型冠狀病毒，包括鑽石公主號郵輪乘客和船員在內，感染人數增至1545人。在疾情擴散下，日本首相安倍晉三表示期待東京奧運按計劃舉辦，強調希望舉辦展示不僅是日本，而是全球戰勝新冠疾情的奧運，又說將會舉辦對運動員和觀眾而言，是安全和安心的奧運。國際奧委會協調委員會主席科茨透露，對判斷奧運舉辦與否，不設期限。他又認為面向奧運的選手選拔活動停滯是最大課題，但強調一切都在為7月24日的開幕而推進。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-17 02:24:43"},{"pid":"b053d225dabfb8e33ddad81c4a6e6ee0e03ab432","tid":1929122,"uid":125380,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:43:53.000Z","msg":"朋友 你返四國食蕉啦"},{"pid":"db647bf4e78369022d12041bb6a4cdf2acb3f5a2","tid":1929122,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"安倍晉三：期待東京奧運按計劃舉辦　展示全球戰勝疫情<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514883-20200317.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514883-20200317.htm&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8J1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=06850542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514883-20200317.htm&h=76198022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514883-20200317.htm</a>"},{"pid":"50ae4ed11033a70b76ebe181227df50695bc10c8","tid":1929122,"uid":8014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:45:25.000Z","msg":"課左金比who 真係講句野都大聲d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1c5467ff3ea09ee70d188c904e2116c7ab88af","tid":1929122,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T18:45:44.000Z","msg":"亞洲準備迎接歐洲回流疫情第二波，邊有咁樂觀6月就完結，7月黎慶祝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"